{"tid":611551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五月天賣飛死機　 售票網：搶票程式攻擊","createTime":"2018-03-31T06:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T06:56:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"13c85d00660a1c75fc3bca0733125234a0acd477","tid":611551,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:31:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180331/20348366\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180331%2F20348366&d=dpqLdsyiDwYmAhPdvKDemv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=ddd0b412\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180331%2F20348366&h=4005dcd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180331/20348366</a><br />\n<br />\n五月天賣飛死機　<br />\n售票網：搶票程式攻擊<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】台灣樂隊「五月天」5月將在香港迪士尼樂園舉行露天演唱會（圖），門票前日開售，至昨清晨前已售罄。前日開售時間因受網上系統故障影響而要延遲，其間系統出現間斷「死機」，令不少歌迷鼓譟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180331/large/a0404a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180331%2Flarge%2Fa0404a.gif&h=2467307a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n集團用程式搶iPhone抽佣<br />\n<br />\n承辦今次售票事宜的「購票通」指是受到搶票程式攻擊，就事件向主辦單位及一眾「五迷」致歉。有專家指，搶票程式即機械人程式，利用程式重複自動填表一次過進行大量購票，但同時會令伺服器不勝負荷而癱瘓。<br />\n購票通（香港）有限公司昨凌晨在官網及fb發通告，指前日因網上售票系統故障，主辦單位「特高娛樂」為公平起見，要求購票通劃一開售時間（包括網上、電話、售票處及手機app購票）。售票系統終於前日中午12時45分重新運作，但發現又受搶票程式攻擊，導致系統緩慢，直至同日下午4時才恢復正常。購票通稱會繼續強化及提升系統，以確保未來運作順暢。<br />\n<br />\n香港資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑稱，搶票程式是一種機械操作自動填表購票的程式，俗稱機械人程式，不同於一般黑客入侵，嚴格來說不算犯法。據悉近年亦有集團利用這類程式為巿民搶購iPhone，從中抽佣5%。方解釋，正常人手輸入資料至少需時1分鐘，但用搶票程式自動填表只須數秒，大量重複使用猶如同一時間多人購票，令伺服器不勝負荷癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\nVXRL電腦保安研究員賴灼東指，巿民安裝某些瀏覽器外掛程式亦能自動填表。他建議在售票網站開始購票步驟首頁及付款頁面，加設俗稱驗證碼的CAPTCHA，分辨人手抑或機械人程式輸入。如發現同一IP地址如機械人般重複購票，所花時間短，有理由懷疑有人用搶票程式，系統可攔截該IP地址。此外，承辦售票的公司應利用多個伺服器進行售票。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張珮琪"},{"pid":"2c313b3a11aa12268c8f555512eaee701961a951","tid":611551,"uid":100276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:34:21.000Z","msg":"Bot"},{"pid":"f362ddf46a6cbe695db1934d922519f3793ddf19","tid":611551,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:47:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba2376ffa03fcaef2a7d62e70e5c72febab9c46d","tid":611551,"uid":48162,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:47:27.000Z","msg":"WFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5ab4199581242da1f8b816201ce37f2d54793e","tid":611551,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:50:45.000Z","msg":"一早要black 程式購票啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ffb0bc1abf9c92481a1cc723c80793189cfc113","tid":611551,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:51:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一早要<span style=\"color: red;\">block</span> 程式購票啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"09adb18c5ac530f2fea01d06568931ddf1ea20ca","tid":611551,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:56:36.000Z","msg":"不過今次真係買到好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e93bc1617af8cb7a6ea85f12e697f9d3a050a11","tid":611551,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ffb0bc1abf9c92481a1cc723c80793189cfc113","tid":611551,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:51:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一早要<span style=\"color: red;\">block</span> 程式購票啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好困難<br />\nAPPLE網都BLOCK唔到"}]}